text: "Parallel Universe" is a 2001 promotional single by Red Hot Chili Peppers and is the second track from their seventh studio album Californication. It went to number 37 on the Billboard Modern Rock Track charts and no music video was released. == References == Category:2001 songs Category:Alternative rock songs Category:Hard rock songs Category:Red Hot Chili Peppers songs
